    "Name": "Maxim APC",
    "Details": "An escort model of the standard Maxim APC, the Maxim Escort trades the troop bay for a heavier weapons load and a Fuel Cell engine. Mimicking the classic Maxim loadout, the Escort has a pair of MML-5's on the front of the vehicle with a third on the rear. A trio of Machine Guns linked together in an array and a Streak SRM-6 are mounted on the turret. Lastly to deter flanking units an SRM-2 Improved Oneshot is mounted on the vehicles flanks.\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Fuel Cell: Improved vehicle engine that works in a Vacuum.</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Movement: 8/12 Hex: 240/360 Meters.</color></b>\n\n<color=#ffcc00><b>Armor:</b> Ferro-Fibrous\n<b>Structure:</b> Structure\n<b>Values       A        S  </b>\n<b>Front</b>       125     25\n<b>Left</b>         115     25\n<b>Right</b>       115     25\n<b>Rear</b>         95     25\n<b>Turret</b>      100     25\n\n<b>Total</b>      550    125</color>\n\n<color=#ff0000>Quirk: Rugged</color>",
